>> Which of the following correctly represents the preconditioning term in RMSProp? <<

( ) [mathjaxinline] v_t = \beta v_{t+1} + (1-\beta) f' (x_t)^2 [/mathjaxinline] {{ The preconditioning term uses [mathjaxinline] v_{t-1} [/mathjaxinline] }}
( ) [mathjaxinline] v_t = \beta v_{t-1} + (1+\beta) f' (x_t)^2 [/mathjaxinline] {{ The preconditioning term uses [mathjaxinline] (1-\beta)[/mathjaxinline]}}
(x) [mathjaxinline] v_t = \beta v_{t-1} + (1-\beta) f' (x_t)^2 [/mathjaxinline]
